Bonus Language	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.GuildWizardOfWaterdeepClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Members of the order study the Art across cultural boundaries. As such, they pick up other languages so that they may enhance their studies. The character may add one additional language to the list of those she already knows. She may include ancient languages (see the section on Language in Chapter 3: Life in Faerun in the FORGOTTEN REALMS Campaign Setting).	KEY:Guild Wizard of Waterdeep ~ Bonus Language									BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Guild Wizard of Waterdeep Language|GuildWizardOfWaterdeepLVL/4																	SORTKEY:Class_Guild_Wizard_Of_Waterdeep	SOURCEPAGE:MoF30	
