Drain Charged Item	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SpellfireChannelerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:As a standard action, a spellfire channeler can drain a single charge from a touched charged item (including single-use items such as potions and scrolls), converting the energy into a single stored spellfire energy level. A fully drained item has no magical properties (a potion becomes water, a scroll becomes blank paper). Only one feature of a multiple-use charged item (such as a scroll with several spells) can be drained per round. A creature gets to make a Will save (DC 10) to prevent one of its held or carried items from being drained.	KEY:Spellfire Channeler ~ Drain Charged Item																										SORTKEY:Class_Spellfire_Channeler	SOURCEPAGE:MoF30	
Increased Storage	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SpellfireChannelerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The channeler's capacity for storing spellfire energy levels is multiplied by the listed value. However, spellfire energy levels in excess of the channeler's Constitution score is dangerous, with different effects depending upon the number of levels stored. Regardless of the number of spellfire energy levels stored, a channeler can voluntarily expend only a number of spellfire energy levels per round equal to her Constitution score. (Involuntary expenditure, such as that noted above, isn't limited in this way.)	KEY:Spellfire Channeler ~ Increased Storage				DEFINE:IncreasedStorageMultiplier|0					BONUS:VAR|IncreasedStorageMultiplier|(SpellfireChanneler+3)/2|TYPE=Base	BONUS:VAR|SpellfireReserve|(max(0,CON)*(IncreasedStorageMultiplier-1))																SORTKEY:Class_Spellfire_Channeler	SOURCEPAGE:MoF30	ASPECT:NAME|Increased Storage|IncrfeasedStorageMultiplier
Improved Healing	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SpellfireChannelerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At 2nd level, the spellfire channeler can release stored spellfire energy levels to heal by touch. This restores 1d4+1 hit points per spellfire energy level expended (rather than the normal 2 points per spellfire energy level).	KEY:Spellfire Channeler ~ Improved Healing																										SORTKEY:Class_Spellfire_Channeler	SOURCEPAGE:MoF30	
