Rapid Blast	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SpellfireChannelerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At 4th level, the spellfire channeler can release two blasts of spellfire as a standard action. This increases to three blasts per standard action at 8th level. Each blast after the first suffers a cumulative -2 penalty to attack rolls (-0 for the first blast, -2 for the second, and -4 for the third).	KEY:Spellfire Channeler ~ Rapid Blast									BONUS:VAR|SpellfireAttacks|SpellfireChanneler/4																	SORTKEY:Class_Spellfire_Channeler	SOURCEPAGE:MoF30	ASPECT:NAME|Rapid Blast %1|(SpellfireChanneler/4)+1
Drain Permanent Item	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SpellfireChannelerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The channeler can drain power from permanent magic items by touch as a standard action. An item that creates spell effects (such as boots of speed) loses that function for 24 hours, and the channeler gains spellfire energy levels equal to half the caster level of the item. A creature gets to make a Will save (DC 10) to prevent one of its held or carried items from being drained. An item with all its permanent abilities drained for the day is still a magic item (for purposes of making saving throws when damaged, and so on).	KEY:Spellfire Channeler ~ Drain Permanent Item																										SORTKEY:Class_Spellfire_Channeler	SOURCEPAGE:MoF30	
Flight	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SpellfireChannelerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The channeler can expend spellfire energy levels to fly as the spell. Each spellfire energy level expended allows the channeler to fly for 1 minute. The flying channeler leaves a visible trail of light that fades after 1 round.	KEY:Spellfire Channeler ~ Flight																										SORTKEY:Class_Spellfire_Channeler	SOURCEPAGE:MoF30	
Deflect Arrows	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SpellfireChannelerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The channeler gains the Deflect Arrows feat, although rather than using a hand, a single spellfire energy level is expended to knock the missile away. If the channeler has no spellfire energy levels available, she cannot use this ability.	KEY:Spellfire Channeler ~ Deflect Arrows																										SORTKEY:Class_Spellfire_Channeler	SOURCEPAGE:MoF30	
Crown of Fire	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SpellfireChannelerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:By expending 10 spellfire energy levels, a channeler can manifest the crown of fire, which appears as a halo of spellfire around her head and provides light equal to a daylight spell. The crown of fire gives her damage reduction 10/+1 and automatically melts all nonmagical weapons that strike her (after inflicting damage, if any). The crown of fire grants the channeler spell resistance 32 (as the spell resistance spell). Maintaining the crown of fire requires expending 10 spellfire energy levels each round, which can be done as a free action. The crown of fire does not interfere with the channeler's actions, including using other spellfire abilities.	KEY:Spellfire Channeler ~ Crown of Fire																										SORTKEY:Class_Spellfire_Channeler	SOURCEPAGE:MoF30	
Maelstrom of Fire	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SpellfireChannelerClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The channeler can release spellfire energy in all directions as a 20-foot-radius spread, dealing 1d6 damage per spellfire energy level expended to all creatures in the area (Reflex half, DC 10 + class level + Charisma modifier).	KEY:Spellfire Channeler ~ Maelstrom of Fire	DESC:Ref DC %1.|MaelstromOfFireDC			DEFINE:MaelstromOfFireDC|0					BONUS:VAR|MaelstromOfFireDC|10+SpellfireChannelerLVL+CHA																	SORTKEY:Class_Spellfire_Channeler	SOURCEPAGE:MoF30	
